---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import MainCard from "@/components/MainCard.astro";
import GitHubStats from "@/components/mdx/GitHubStats.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <MainCard
    title="About Me"
    description="Open-source enthusiast and Linux advocate."
    textOverlay="ABOUT"
    infoIcon="lucide:user"
  >
    <div class="space-y-10 mb-8">
      <!-- Profile Section -->
      <section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
        <div class="avatar">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-xl ring ring-primary ring-offset-base-100 ring-offset-2 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="https://blog.ninebytes.top/profile.png" alt="https://blog.ninebytes.top/profile.png" width="160" height="160" loading="eager" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">NineBytes</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-base-content/80 mb-4">Open-source enthusiast and Linux advocate.</p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start mb-6">
            <a href="https://github.com/ninebytes687" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline gap-2">
              <Icon name="lucide:github" class="w-4 h-4" />
              <span>GitHub</span>
            </a>
            <div class="btn btn-sm btn-outline gap-2 cursor-default">
                <Icon name="lucide:twitter" class="w-4 h-4" />
                <span>Twitter[Disable]</span>
            </div>
            <a href="mailto:ninebytes@ninebytes.top" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline gap-2">
              <Icon name="lucide:mail" class="w-4 h-4" />
              <span>Email</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="text-base-content/80">
            00s | Computer technology enthusiasts | Linux geek 🐧
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- Who am I Section -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <Icon name="lucide:user" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
        <span>Who am i ?</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          普普通通三线城市的00后，这里主要记录了我的一些技术 <del>没什么技术含量</del>、生活、学习等方面的文章。
        </p>
        <br>
        <p>
          博客项目使用的是<b><a href="https://astro.build/"><span style="text-decoration: underline yellow; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;">Astro</span></a></b>架构，使用<b><a href="https://github.com/EveSunMaple/Frosti"><span style="text-decoration: underline yellow; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;">Frosti</span></a></b>主题，托管在Github，使用赛博大善人CloudFlare Workers构建。
        </p>
      </section>
      <!-- Who am I Section End-->

      <!-- Blog Theme Tech Stack -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <Icon name="lucide:code-2" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
          <span>Blog Theme Tech Stack</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
          {
            [
              { name: "Astro", icon: "simple-icons:astro", color: "oklch(0.5 0.2 300)" },
              { name: "JavaScript", icon: "simple-icons:javascript", color: "oklch(0.8 0.2 80)" },
              { name: "TypeScript", icon: "simple-icons:typescript", color: "oklch(0.6 0.2 250)" },
              { name: "React", icon: "simple-icons:react", color: "oklch(0.7 0.2 200)" },
              { name: "Node.js", icon: "simple-icons:nodedotjs", color: "oklch(0.7 0.2 140)" },
              { name: "TailwindCSS", icon: "simple-icons:tailwindcss", color: "oklch(0.6 0.2 220)" },
              { name: "HTML5", icon: "simple-icons:html5", color: "oklch(0.7 0.2 30)" },
              { name: "CSS3", icon: "simple-icons:css3", color: "oklch(0.7 0.2 220)" },
              { name: "Git", icon: "simple-icons:git", color: "oklch(0.7 0.2 30)" },
              { name: "C++", icon: "simple-icons:cplusplus", color: "oklch(0.6 0.2 240)" },
              { name: "C#", icon: "simple-icons:csharp", color: "oklch(0.6 0.2 160)" },
              { name: "Python", icon: "simple-icons:python", color: "oklch(0.7 0.2 250)" },
            ].map((tech) => (
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-2" style={`color: ${tech.color}`}>
                  <Icon name={tech.icon} class="w-10 h-10" />
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">{tech.name}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Blog Theme Tech Stack End-->

      <!-- Timeline Section -->
      <section class="space-y-8 mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <Icon name="lucide:history" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
          <span>Website Timeline</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
            <Icon name="lucide:activity" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2025年8月3日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">博客接入Umami Cloud统计</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">高效、易读、可视化站点统计</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
            <Icon name="lucide:calendar-days" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2025年5月26日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">about pages增加Website Timeline</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">可视化呈现技术栈迭代与关键里程碑</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:cloudflare" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2025年5月8日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">CNAME CloudFlare Pages</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">优化全球访问速度，适应国内网络环境</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
              <Icon name="simple-icons:astro" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年12月31日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">重构为Astro静态站点</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">采用Frosti主题，显著提升性能表现</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
              <Icon name="lucide:rocket" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年10月11日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">使用更为轻便的TypeCho Cuckoo主题</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">轻量化设计带来显著性能提升</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-black">
              <Icon name="lucide:panel-top" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-primary/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年9月2日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">使用WordPress Argon主题</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">美观但系统消耗资源较大</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
              <Icon name="lucide:link" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年7月31日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">注册namesilo top域名</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">花费$1.88巨款</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-black">
              <Icon name="lucide:shield-check" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-secondary/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年7月16日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">实现全站HTTPS加密</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">提升数据安全性</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-accent-content">
              <Icon name="lucide:link" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-px h-full bg-accent/30 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年7月15日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">注册.us.kg域名</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">免费，但容易被GFW</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#84ccd3] text-success-content">
              <Icon name="lucide:globe" class="w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024年7月14日</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">突然萌生搭建一个属于自己博客的想法</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-1">开始寻找现有博客框架</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Timeline Section End -->

      <!-- Others Section -->
      <section class="space-y-4 mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
      <Icon name="lucide:info" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
      <span>Others</span>
      </h2>

        <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-base-content/80">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">版权声明</h3>
      <p>
      本博客所有原创内容（包括文章、图片、代码等）版权归
      <a href="https://blog.ninebytes.top/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link link-primary font-semibold">
        NineBytes
      </a> 
        所有，采用
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link link-primary">
        CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
      </a>
      许可协议。转载文章请注明文章出处。
      </p>
    
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-4">侵权声明</h3>
      <p>
      本站部分内容可能来源于网络，仅供学习交流。如无意中侵犯了您的权益，请通过以下方式联系删除：
      <br />
      邮箱📧📧：<a href="mailto:ninebytes@ninebytes.top" class="link link-primary">ninebytes@ninebytes.top</a>
      <br />
      （请提供具体链接及权属证明，我们将在核实后48小时内处理。）
      </p>
    
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-4">隐私声明</h3>
      <p>
      本站使用Umami进行统计，仅收集匿名数据（如国家与浏览量），不会关联个人身份与精确IP。请您放心浏览，希望您能在这里发现有价值的内容，享受阅读的乐趣。
      </p>
    
      <!-- English Section Divider -->
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-4">Copyright Notice</h3>
      <p>
      All original content on this blog (including articles, images, code, etc.) is copyrighted by
      <a href="https://blog.ninebytes.top/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link link-primary font-semibold">
        NineBytes
      </a> 
      and licensed under
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link link-primary">
        CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
      </a>
      . Please indicate the source when reposting.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-4">Infringement Notice</h3>
      <p>
      Some content may originate from the internet for educational purposes only. If you believe your rights have been inadvertently infringed, please contact us for removal:
      <br />
      Email📧📧: <a href="mailto:ninebytes@ninebytes.top" class="link link-primary">ninebytes@ninebytes.top</a>
      <br />
      (Please provide specific URLs and proof of ownership. We will process your request within 48 hours after verification.)
      </p>
    
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-4">Privacy Notice</h3>
      <p>
      This website uses Umami for analytics, collecting only anonymous data such as country and page views. It does not link any information to individual identities or exact IP addresses. Feel free to browse with peace of mind. We hope you discover valuable content here and enjoy your reading experience.
      </p>

      <div class="not-prose mt-6">
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost gap-2">
      <Icon name="simple-icons:creativecommons" class="w-4 h-4" />
      <span>CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Others Section End -->

    </div>
  </MainCard>
</BaseLayout>
